snippet.title: Sunset Overdrive E3 Teaser
snippet.description:
From Insomniac Games comes Sunset Overdrive.  A catastrophic event has left your city overrun by mutants, but while most perish or transform, you flourish. It turns out your calling isn't picking up trash or serving food, it's mutant destruction. 

ESRB Rating: RATING PENDING

Pre-Order here www.xbox.com/SunsetOverdrive
